bilingual.source: Cang Jie is the legendary creator of Chinese characters.
bilingual.target: 仓颉是传说中的汉字创造者。

bilingual.source: The creator of the software is giving a talk today.
bilingual.target: 这个软件的创造者今天要做一个演讲。

bilingual.source: The creator of the new app is a young entrepreneur.
bilingual.target: 这个新应用的创造者是一位年轻的企业家。

bilingual.source: The creator of the artwork explained his inspiration.
bilingual.target: 这件艺术品的创造者解释了他的灵感来源。

bilingual.source: She is known as the creator of several popular TV shows.
bilingual.target: 她被称为几部热门电视节目的创造者。

bilingual.source: Many Hindus believe that Brahma is the creator of the universe.
bilingual.target: 许多印度教徒相信梵天是宇宙的创造者。

bilingual.source: In many cultures, God is seen as the creator of the universe.
bilingual.target: 在许多文化中，上帝被视为宇宙的创造者。

bilingual.source: The creator of the famous comic book series will be at the convention.
bilingual.target: 著名漫画系列的创造者将出席这次大会。

bilingual.source: The ancient texts often refer to Elohim as the creator of the universe.
bilingual.target: 古代文本常常提到上帝是宇宙的创造者。

bilingual.source: In ancient Greek philosophy, the demiurge is considered the creator of the universe.
bilingual.target: 在古希腊哲学中，造物主被认为是宇宙的创造者。

list.abstract: creator，全称广州市天誉创高电子科技有限公司，成立于2006年，公司总部位于广东省广州市，梁柱浓任公司执行董事，是一家集研发、生产、销售和服务于一体的音视频整体解决方案提供商与产品国际制造商。 该公司代表产品有ECIS布式坐席协作管理系统、ESPMAX列拼接处理器等。 2020年，creator成功进入COK杯·2020声光视讯行业品牌评选企业30强。

yingyinNormal.en: Who else knows of this map? No one, but Byamba, myself, and its creator.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还有谁知道这幅地图？就只有宾巴，我，还有此图的绘制者。

yingyinNormal.en: You took the dot back to the main screen and that's when you found the first Easter egg ever put in a video game. The creator's name.
yingyinNormal.zh: 把方块拖回到主屏幕你就能找到游戏史上第一个彩蛋。那就是设计者的名字。
